title: Why don't YOU like playing jungle??  I choose mid and top and still get auotfilled to jungle. WHY???
body:
Do you know how hard it is to get a mid game and then have it go through without someone dodging because SOMEONE got autofilled to jungle.
Does anyone queue up for jg at all? Also don't flame me if you get stomped in lane in YOUR MAIN ROLE and say *report jg no gank* Lol. I didn't even want the fucking role to begin with. I chose mid and top for my roles and would rather play top then jungle at this point. PLEASE PLAY JUNGLE FOR ONCE, PEOPLE!!!
